# Build context for fly-remote/fullresolve/Dockerfile is this dir (e2e/reference/codex).
# The Dockerfile COPYs only: local-docker/{run-benchmark.py,Dockerfile.instance,
# Dockerfile.toolbox,context}, report-runs.py, fly-remote/fullresolve/entrypoint.sh.
# Everything below is local-only noise that would bloat the remote-builder upload.
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/.unerr
**/.codex
local-docker/logs
local-docker/results
local-docker/grading
fly-remote/out
fly-remote/**/out
**/*.log
.DS_Store
